The {{{<<float>>}}} macro raises a {{{Wiki macro error:}}} when it contains text with non-english characters.

The following works ok:

{{{\\
<<float left>>\\
Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.

<</float>>\\
}}}

The following example contains spanish text with an acute accent and doesn&#x27;t work:

{{{\\
<<float left>>\\
Yo para ser feliz quiero un camión.

<</float>>\\
}}}

